fulltitle: ECM50 | 1961 Carla Bley and Steve Swallow on Jimmy Giuffe 3
title: ECM50 | 1961 Carla Bley and Steve Swallow on Jimmy Giuffe 3
description:
Filmed in Willow, New York, September 2019
ECM50 | 1969-2019 is a series of 50+1 documentary short films by IJB
(version without music, for copyright reasons / VERSION WITH MUSIC HERE: https://vimeo.com/389577838 )

Jimmy Giuffre 3 "1961" (includes "Fusion" and "Thesis"):
Jimmy Giuffre, clarinet /  Paul Bley, piano / Steve Swallow, double-bass
Recorded New York 1961
Engineer: Dick Olmstead 
Originally released on Verve 196,  produced by Creed Taylor
Remixed June 1990, Rainbow Studio, Oslo, Jan Erik Kongshaug, Manfred Eicher

Photos: Herb Snitzer 
Re-Release Cover Design: Barbara Wojirsch
Reissue ECM 1438/39 produced by Manfred Eicher, Jean-Philippe Allard
Released on ECM Records 1992 
© 1992 ECM Records GmbH
